## Limitations

The findings are based on publicly available online resources, which may not cover all aspects of community influence comprehensively. The perspectives are primarily anecdotal and may lack empirical backing. Additionally, the information is limited to the context provided by the sources, which may not reflect broader societal trends. Further research, including academic studies and empirical data, would provide a more robust understanding of the topic.